Package: acleddata
Type: Package
Title: Download the Armed Conflict Location and Event Dataset (ACLED) from the new API
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Guy", "Schvitz",
      email = "guy.schvitz@ec.europa.eu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package includes functions to download the Armed Conflict Location and Event Dataset (ACLED) through the new API, launched in August 2025. It includes a function to request an access token, get an overview of all ACLED region codes and to download ACLED data. 
